bilingual.source: There's some gunk stuck in the drain.
bilingual.target: 排水口卡住了一些污垢。

bilingual.source: There was a floater blocking the drain.
bilingual.target: 有一个漂浮物堵住了排水口。

bilingual.source: The bathtub takes a long time to drain.
bilingual.target: 浴缸需要很长时间才能排水。

bilingual.source: He forgot to drain the water from the cooler.
bilingual.target: 他忘了从冷却器中排水。

bilingual.source: She watched the water swirling down the drain.
bilingual.target: 她看着水在排水口旋转。

bilingual.source: You can drain the water through this outlet.
bilingual.target: 你可以通过这个排出口排水。

bilingual.source: The drain blockage caused the bathroom to flood.
bilingual.target: 排水管阻塞导致浴室淹水。

bilingual.source: The sink overflowed due to a clogged drain.
bilingual.target: 因为排水管堵塞，水槽溢出了。

bilingual.source: She used the plunger to clear the sink drain.
bilingual.target: 她用马桶吸盘清理水槽的排水管。

list.abstract: 《Drain》是1996年发行的一首歌曲，演唱者是X JAPAN。
Drain又叫做通渠剂，主要成分是氢氧化钠，属碱性，具腐蚀性。通常遇水后可产生高热，，溶解积聚或凝固油渍，以及其他淤积物。

yingyinNormal.en: God, look what I found in the drain. What?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，你看我在排水管里发现什么？什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig has dropped the car keys down a drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 车钥匙从猪爸爸的手里掉进排水道了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, you'll never get those back. That drain's really deep. What are drains for? A drain takes the rain water away to the sea.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你们再也找不回来了，这个排水道非常非常深。排水道有什么用处啊？排水道能把雨水排走排到大海里。

yingyinNormal.zh: 那你们再也找不回来了，这个排水道非常非常深。排水道有什么用处啊？排水道能把雨水排走排到大海里。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh dear. Daddy Pig has dropped the car keys down a drain. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，糟糕，车钥匙从猪爸爸的手里掉进排水道了。哦！

yingyinNormal.en: The drain must be deeper than I thought. The stick is not long enough to reach the keys.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，这排水道比我想象的要深啊。棍子不够长，根本够不到钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: The drain must be deeper than I thought. The stick is not long enough to reach the keys.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗯，这排水道比我想象的要深啊。棍子不够长，根本够不到钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: The fishing line is not long enough to reach the keys. My goodness. How deep is this drain?
yingyinNormal.zh: 鱼线也不够长，还是够不到车钥匙。我的天啊，这排水道到底有多深啊？

yingyinNormal.en: The fishing line is not long enough to reach the keys. My goodness. How deep is this drain?
yingyinNormal.zh: 鱼线也不够长，还是够不到车钥匙。我的天啊，这排水道到底有多深啊？

yingyinNormal.en: We are not fishing for fish. We are fishing for keys. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要钓鱼，我们要钓车钥匙。我们的爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: We are not fishing for fish. We are fishing for keys. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要钓鱼，我们要钓车钥匙。我们的爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. Let's go home. That might be difficult. Why? Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 弄好了，我们回家吧。额，这恐怕有一点点苦难哪。为什么？爸爸他把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. Let's go home. That might be difficult. Why? Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 弄好了，我们回家吧。额，这恐怕有一点点苦难哪。为什么？爸爸他把车钥匙掉进排水道里了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's weird, but you know what I don't wanna throw this away. I mean this is like all I have left of him, gross, drain hair. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 奇怪，但我并不想把它丢掉,这些是我仅有的属于他的东西，恶心的排水管的头发。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Bull is digging up the beauty spot. Stop. What's going on? We came to see the beauty spot. They're digging it up now. Won't be long. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 公牛先生要把大山风景区的路挖开。停车！出什么事了？我们是来大山风景区游玩的。额，他们现在正在挖路呢，很快就好。因为我爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里去了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Bull is digging up the beauty spot. Stop. What's going on? We came to see the beauty spot. They're digging it up now. Won't be long. My Daddy dropped the car keys down the drain. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 公牛先生要把大山风景区的路挖开。停车！出什么事了？我们是来大山风景区游玩的。额，他们现在正在挖路呢，很快就好。因为我爸爸把车钥匙掉进排水道里去了。哦！

yingyinNormal.en: Come on. We hate it here. I cannot look at that red hair in the shower drain one more second. Look around here, people. None of us have red hair.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别这样，我们恨死这里了，我多一秒都不想再瞧见浴室排水槽里的红发了，睁大眼睛瞧瞧 我们几个没人是红头发。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry. I'll get the car keys out of the drain with a stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心，我可以用棍子把钥匙从下面弄出来。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Daddy Pig. Don't worry. I'll get the car keys out of the drain with a stick. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，天呢，猪爸爸！别担心，我可以用棍子把钥匙从下面弄出来。好耶！

yingyinNormal.en: And then really that's ready. So you can either drain it or transfer it straight to the plate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就可以出锅了，可以沥干一会儿，也可直接装盘。
